{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882864015,"sessionID":"ses_285222e43ffe4HfnmS1LBKuzWs","part":{"id":"prt_d7addf2ce001AIH4ifENe8myCg","messageID":"msg_d7adde8460013byXPzCH6uxzwV","sessionID":"ses_285222e43ffe4HfnmS1LBKuzWs","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_7464ec9a59d7473cb11754af","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-033/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-033/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-033: Makefile 构建目标体系\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: 本提案实现 AgentCube 项目的 Makefile 构建目标体系，为 Docker 镜像构建、推送、验证、测试提供标准化的自动化命令。该 Makefile 是 AgentCube 容器化工作流的核心入口，支撑开发、CI/CD、生产环境的镜像生命周期管理。\n6: \n7: 目标是：\n8: \n9: 1. **构建自动化** - 提供统一的 `make` 命令简化 Docker 镜像构建流程，减少手动操作错误\n10: 2. **目标分层** - 支持全量构建 (`docker-build-all`) 和单组件构建 (`docker-build-workloadmanager` 等)，适应不同场景\n11: 3. **推送标准化** - 统一镜像推送流程，自动关联 VERSION、COMMIT_SHA、DOCKER_TAG 多标签\n12: 4. **集群集成** - 提供 Kind 集群加载目标 (`kind-load-all`)，支持本地开发测试\n13: 5. **多架构支持** - 集成 Docker Buildx，支持 amd64、arm64 多架构镜像构建\n14: 6. **质量门禁** - 内置镜像验证 (`docker-validate`) 和测试 (`docker-test`) 目标，确保镜像质量\n15: 7. **清理工具** - 提供本地镜像清理目标 (`docker-clean`)，减少磁盘占用\n16: \n17: 本提案基于 existing Makefile (仅包含 Docker 相关目标) 进行扩展，遵循 Makefile 最佳实践和 AR-032 Dockerfile 多阶段构建规范。\n18: \n19: ## Scope\n20: \n21: **Module:** root  \n22: **Language:** Makefile  \n23: **Size:** M\n24: \n25: 本 AR 包含：\n26: \n27: - **包含内容：**\n28:   - Makefile 根文件更新 - 扩展构建目标体系\n29:   - 构建目标 (build) - `docker-build-all`, `docker-build-*`\n30:   - 推送目标 (push) - `docker-push-all`, `docker-push-*`\n31:   - Kind 加载目标 (kind-load) - `kind-load-all`, `kind-load-*`\n32:   - 多架构目标 (buildx) - `docker-buildx-all`, `docker-buildx-*`\n33:   - 验证目标 (validate) - `docker-validate`, `docker-validate-*`\n34:   - 测试目标 (test) - `docker-test`, `docker-test-build`, `docker-test-runtime`\n35:   - 清理目标 (clean) - `docker-clean`\n36:   - 帮助目标 (help) - 打印可用目标和变量\n37:   - 配置变量 - `DOCKER_REGISTRY`, `DOCKER_TAG`, `VERSION`, `COMMIT_SHA`\n38: \n39: - **不包含内容：**\n40:   - Dockerfile 编写（由 AR-032 管理）\n41:   - Helm Chart 构建（由 AR-030 管理）\n42:   - CI/CD 流水线配置\n43:   - Go/Python 应用编译目标（已有独立 Makefile 或命令）\n44: \n45: ## Current State Analysis\n46: \n47: ### 现有 Makefile 状态\n48: \n49: 根据根目录 `Makefile` (237 行)，当前已实现：\n50: \n51: **已有目标：**\n52: - `docker-build-all`, `docker-build-workloadmanager`, `docker-build-router`, `docker-build-picod` - 构建目标\n53: - `docker-push-all`, `docker-push-workloadmanager`, `docker-push-router`, `docker-push-picod` - 推送目标\n54: - `kind-load-all`, `kind-load-workloadmanager`, `kind-load-router`, `kind-load-picod` - Kind 加载目标\n55: - `docker-buildx-all`, `docker-buildx-workloadmanager`, `docker-buildx-router`, `docker-buildx-picod` - 多架构目标\n56: - `docker-clean` - 清理目标\n57: - `docker-validate`, `docker-validate-*` - 验证目标\n58: - `docker-test`, `docker-test-build`, `docker-test-runtime` - 测试目标\n59: - `help` - 帮助信息\n60: \n61: **已有变量：**\n62: - `DOCKER_REGISTRY` (默认：ghcr.io/volcano-sh)\n63: - `DOCKER_TAG` (默认：latest)\n64: - `VERSION` (从 git tag 获取)\n65: - `COMMIT_SHA` (从 git rev-parse 获取)\n66: \n67: **镜像命名：**\n68: - `WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE` = $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/workloadmanager\n69: - `ROUTER_IMAGE` = $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/router\n70: - `PICOD_IMAGE` = $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/picod\n71: \n72: ### 差距分析\n73: \n74: 当前 Makefile 已经比较完善，但根据 AR-033 的\"构建目标体系\"要求，需要：\n75: \n76: 1. **目标文档化** - 缺少目标依赖关系图和执行顺序说明\n77: 2. **测试脚本集成** - 验证脚本和测试脚本依赖外部文件 (`deployment/docker/test/validate.sh` 等)，需要确保这些文件存在\n78: 3. **错误处理** - 部分目标缺少错误处理（如 `docker-clean` 使用 `-` 前缀忽略错误，但其他目标未处理）\n79: 4. **可扩展性** - 新增组件时需要手动添加多个目标，缺少自动化生成机制\n80: 5. **PHONY 声明** - 所有目标都已声明为 `.PHONY`，符合最佳实践\n81: \n82: ### 参考设计规范\n83: \n84: 根据 AR-032 proposal.md 和项目结构：\n85: \n86: **Makefile 要求：**\n87: - 支持三个组件：Workload Manager、Router、Picod\n88: - 镜像标签：latest, <commit-sha>, <version>\n89: - 基础镜像：distroless/static-debian11\n90: - 构建优化：多阶段构建，CGO_ENABLED=0\n91: \n92: **验证脚本要求：**\n93: - 检查镜像大小 (< 50MB)\n94: - 检查层数 (<= 5)\n95: - 检查非 root 用户\n96: - 检查端口暴露\n97: - 检查健康检查配置\n98: \n99: ### 需要补充的文件\n100: \n101: 根据 Makefile 中引用的脚本：\n102: \n103: 1. `deployment/docker/test/validate.sh` - 镜像验证脚本\n104: 2. `deployment/docker/test/build_test.sh` - 构建测试脚本\n105: 3. `deployment/docker/test/runtime_test.sh` - 运行时测试脚本\n106: \n107: 这些脚本当前不存在，需要创建。\n108: \n109: ## Proposed Changes\n110: \n111: ### 1. Makefile 目标体系结构\n112: \n113: ```\n114: Makefile 目标层次结构\n115: \n116: 1. 构建目标 (Build)\n117:    ├── docker-build-all           # 构建所有镜像\n118:    ├── docker-build-workloadmanager\n119:    ├── docker-build-router\n120:    └── docker-build-picod\n121: \n122: 2. 推送目标 (Push)\n123:    ├── docker-push-all            # 推送所有镜像\n124:    ├── docker-push-workloadmanager\n125:    ├── docker-push-router\n126:    └── docker-push-picod\n127: \n128: 3. Kind 加载目标 (Kind Load)\n129:    ├── kind-load-all              # 加载所有镜像到 Kind\n130:    ├── kind-load-workloadmanager\n131:    ├── kind-load-router\n132:    └── kind-load-picod\n133: \n134: 4. 多架构目标 (Buildx)\n135:    ├── docker-buildx-all          # 多架构构建所有\n136:    ├── docker-buildx-workloadmanager\n137:    ├── docker-buildx-router\n138:    └── docker-buildx-picod\n139: \n140: 5. 验证目标 (Validate)\n141:    ├── docker-validate            # 验证所有镜像\n142:    ├── docker-validate-workloadmanager\n143:    ├── docker-validate-router\n144:    └── docker-validate-picod\n145: \n146: 6. 测试目标 (Test)\n147:    ├── docker-test                # 运行所有测试\n148:    ├── docker-test-build          # 构建测试\n149:    └── docker-test-runtime        # 运行时测试\n150: \n151: 7. 清理目标 (Clean)\n152:    └── docker-clean               # 清理本地镜像\n153: \n154: 8. 帮助目标 (Help)\n155:    └── help                       # 打印帮助信息\n156: ```\n157: \n158: ### 2. 现有 Makefile 保持不变\n159: \n160: 当前 Makefile 已经实现了完整的目标体系，无需修改。重点补充缺失的脚本文件。\n161: \n162: ### 3. 创建验证脚本\n163: \n164: ```bash\n165: #!/bin/bash\n166: # deployment/docker/test/validate.sh\n167: # Validate Docker image for size, layers, security, ports, healthcheck\n168: \n169: set -e\n170: \n171: IMAGE=\"${1:-}\"\n172: \n173: if [ -z \"$IMAGE\" ]; then\n174:     echo \"Usage: $0 <image-name>\"\n175:     exit 1\n176: fi\n177: \n178: echo \"Validating image: $IMAGE\"\n179: echo \"\"\n180: \n181: # Check if image exists\n182: if ! docker image inspect \"$IMAGE\" > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n183:     echo \"✗ Image not found: $IMAGE\"\n184:     exit 1\n185: fi\n186: echo \"✓ Image exists\"\n187: \n188: # Check image size (< 50MB)\n189: SIZE=$(docker image inspect \"$IMAGE\" --format='{{.Size}}')\n190: SIZE_MB=$((SIZE / 1024 / 1024))\n191: if [ $SIZE_MB -lt 50 ]; then\n192:     echo \"✓ Image size: ${SIZE_MB}MB (< 50MB)\"\n193: else\n194:     echo \"✗ Image size: ${SIZE_MB}MB (>= 50MB)\"\n195:     exit 1\n196: fi\n197: \n198: # Check layer count (<= 5)\n199: LAYERS=$(docker image history \"$IMAGE\" --format='{{.ID}}' | wc -l)\n200: if [ $LAYERS -le 5 ]; then\n201:     echo \"✓ Layer count: $LAYERS (<= 5)\"\n202: else\n203:     echo \"✗ Layer count: $LAYERS (> 5)\"\n204:     exit 1\n205: fi\n206: \n207: # Check non-root user\n208: USER_SPEC=$(docker image inspect \"$IMAGE\" --format='{{.Config.User}}')\n209: if [ -n \"$USER_SPEC\" ] && [ \"$USER_SPEC\" != \"root\" ]; then\n210:     echo \"✓ Running as non-root: $USER_SPEC\"\n211: else\n212:     echo \"✗ Running as root or no user specified\"\n213:     exit 1\n214: fi\n215: \n216: # Check exposed ports\n217: PORTS=$(docker image inspect \"$IMAGE\" --format='{{json .Config.ExposedPorts}}')\n218: if echo \"$PORTS\" | grep -q \"8080\"; then\n219:     echo \"✓ Port 8080 exposed\"\n220: else\n221:     echo \"✗ Port 8080 not exposed\"\n222:     exit 1\n223: fi\n224: \n225: # Check healthcheck\n226: HEALTHCHECK=$(docker image inspect \"$IMAGE\" --format='{{json .Config.Healthcheck}}')\n227: if [ \"$HEALTHCHECK\" != \"null\" ] && [ -n \"$HEALTHCHECK\" ]; then\n228:     echo \"✓ Health check configured\"\n229: else\n230:     echo \"✗ Health check not configured\"\n231:     exit 1\n232: fi\n233: \n234: echo \"\"\n235: echo \"All validations passed!\"\n236: ```\n237: \n238: ### 4. 创建构建测试脚本\n239: \n240: ```bash\n241: #!/bin/bash\n242: # deployment/docker/test/build_test.sh\n243: # Test Docker image build process\n244: \n245: set -e\n246: \n247: echo \"Running Docker build tests...\"\n248: echo \"\"\n249: \n250: # Test 1: Check Dockerfile exists\n251: echo \"Test 1: Checking Dockerfile existence...\"\n252: DOCKERFILES=(\n253:     \"deployment/docker/Dockerfile\"\n254:     \"deployment/docker/Dockerfile.router\"\n255:     \"deployment/docker/Dockerfile.picod\"\n256: )\n257: \n258: for dockerfile in \"${DOCKERFILES[@]}\"; do\n259:     if [ -f \"$dockerfile\" ]; then\n260:         echo \"  ✓ $dockerfile exists\"\n261:     else\n262:         echo \"  ✗ $dockerfile not found\"\n263:         exit 1\n264:     fi\n265: done\n266: \n267: # Test 2: Check Makefile targets\n268: echo \"\"\n269: echo \"Test 2: Checking Makefile targets...\"\n270: if make -n docker-build-all > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n271:     echo \"  ✓ docker-build-all target available\"\n272: else\n273:     echo \"  ✗ docker-build-all target not found\"\n274:     exit 1\n275: fi\n276: \n277: # Test 3: Check Docker daemon\n278: echo \"\"\n279: echo \"Test 3: Checking Docker daemon...\"\n280: if docker info > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n281:     echo \"  ✓ Docker daemon is running\"\n282: else\n283:     echo \"  ✗ Docker daemon is not running\"\n284:     exit 1\n285: fi\n286: \n287: # Test 4: Check buildx availability\n288: echo \"\"\n289: echo \"Test 4: Checking Docker buildx...\"\n290: if docker buildx version > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n291:     echo \"  ✓ Docker buildx is available\"\n292: else\n293:     echo \"  ✗ Docker buildx not found (optional)\"\n294: fi\n295: \n296: echo \"\"\n297: echo \"All build tests passed!\"\n298: ```\n299: \n300: ### 5. 创建运行时测试脚本\n301: \n302: ```bash\n303: #!/bin/bash\n304: # deployment/docker/test/runtime_test.sh\n305: # Test Docker container runtime behavior\n306: \n307: set -e\n308: \n309: echo \"Running Docker runtime tests...\"\n310: echo \"\"\n311: \n312: # Test 1: Container starts successfully\n313: echo \"Test 1: Testing container startup...\"\n314: TEST_IMAGE=\"${TEST_IMAGE:-ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager:latest}\"\n315: \n316: CONTAINER_ID=$(docker run -d --rm \"$TEST_IMAGE\" --help 2>/dev/null || true)\n317: if [ -n \"$CONTAINER_ID\" ]; then\n318:     echo \"  ✓ Container started successfully\"\n319:     docker stop \"$CONTAINER_ID\" 2>/dev/null || true\n320: else\n321:     echo \"  ⚠ Container startup test skipped (image may not exist)\"\n322: fi\n323: \n324: # Test 2: Health check configuration\n325: echo \"\"\n326: echo \"Test 2: Checking health check configuration...\"\n327: HEALTHCHECK=$(docker image inspect \"$TEST_IMAGE\" --format='{{json .Config.Healthcheck}}' 2>/dev/null || echo \"null\")\n328: if [ \"$HEALTHCHECK\" != \"null\" ]; then\n329:     echo \"  ✓ Health check is configured\"\n330: else\n331:     echo \"  ⚠ Health check not configured (image may not exist)\"\n332: fi\n333: \n334: # Test 3: Port exposure\n335: echo \"\"\n336: echo \"Test 3: Checking port exposure...\"\n337: PORTS=$(docker image inspect \"$TEST_IMAGE\" --format='{{json .Config.ExposedPorts}}' 2>/dev/null || echo \"null\")\n338: if echo \"$PORTS\" | grep -q \"8080\"; then\n339:     echo \"  ✓ Port 8080 is exposed\"\n340: else\n341:     echo \"  ⚠ Port 8080 not exposed (image may not exist)\"\n342: fi\n343: \n344: # Test 4: Non-root user\n345: echo \"\"\n346: echo \"Test 4: Checking non-root user...\"\n347: USER_SPEC=$(docker image inspect \"$TEST_IMAGE\" --format='{{.Config.User}}' 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\n348: if [ -n \"$USER_SPEC\" ] && [ \"$USER_SPEC\" != \"root\" ]; then\n349:     echo \"  ✓ Running as non-root: $USER_SPEC\"\n350: else\n351:     echo \"  ⚠ Root user or no user specified (image may not exist)\"\n352: fi\n353: \n354: echo \"\"\n355: echo \"All runtime tests completed!\"\n356: ```\n357: \n358: ### 6. 创建脚本执行权限\n359: \n360: ```bash\n361: chmod +x deployment/docker/test/validate.sh\n362: chmod +x deployment/docker/test/build_test.sh\n363: chmod +x deployment/docker/test/runtime_test.sh\n364: ```\n365: \n366: ### 7. 目录结构\n367: \n368: ```\n369: deployment/docker/test/\n370: ├── validate.sh        # 镜像验证脚本\n371: ├── build_test.sh      # 构建测试脚本\n372: └── runtime_test.sh    # 运行时测试脚本\n373: ```\n374: \n375: ### 8. Makefile 更新（可选增强）\n376: \n377: 如需增强 Makefile，可添加以下目标：\n378: \n379: ```makefile\n380: # 新增：检查依赖\n381: .PHONY: check-docker\n382: check-docker:\n383: \t@command -v docker >/dev/null 2>&1 || { echo \"Docker is required but not installed.\"; exit 1; }\n384: \n385: .PHONY: check-buildx\n386: check-buildx:\n387: \t@docker buildx version >/dev/null 2>&1 || { echo \"Docker buildx is required.\"; exit 1; }\n388: \n389: # 新增：预检查\n390: .PHONY: prereqs\n391: prereqs: check-docker\n392: \t@echo \"✓ All prerequisites met\"\n393: \n394: # 新增：完整 CI 流程\n395: .PHONY: ci\n396: ci: prereqs docker-test docker-build-all docker-validate\n397: \t@echo \"✓ CI pipeline completed\"\n398: ```\n399: \n400: ## Impact Analysis\n401: \n402: ### 依赖影响\n403: \n404: | 依赖项 | 版本 | 用途 |\n405: |--------|------|------|\n406: | GNU Make | ≥3.81 | 构建自动化 |\n407: | Docker | ≥20.10 | 镜像构建和运行 |\n408: | Docker Buildx | ≥0.6 | 多架构构建（可选） |\n409: | Kind | ≥0.11 | 本地 Kubernetes 集群（可选） |\n410: | Bash | ≥4.0 | 脚本执行 |\n411: | Git | 任意 | 版本信息获取 |\n412: \n413: ### 模块依赖关系\n414: \n415: ```\n416: Makefile (根目录)\n417: ├── deployment/docker/Dockerfile           # Workload Manager Dockerfile (AR-032)\n418: ├── deployment/docker/Dockerfile.router    # Router Dockerfile (AR-032)\n419: ├── deployment/docker/Dockerfile.picod     # Picod Dockerfile (AR-032)\n420: ├── deployment/docker/test/validate.sh     # 镜像验证脚本 (本 AR 新增)\n421: ├── deployment/docker/test/build_test.sh   # 构建测试脚本 (本 AR 新增)\n422: └── deployment/docker/test/runtime_test.sh # 运行时测试脚本 (本 AR 新增)\n423: ```\n424: \n425: ### 向后兼容性\n426: \n427: - 现有 Makefile 目标保持不变\n428: - 新增脚本文件不影响现有功能\n429: - 环境变量使用默认值，向后兼容\n430: \n431: ### 测试影响\n432: \n433: - 需要验证 Makefile 目标可正常执行\n434: - 需要验证脚本文件有执行权限\n435: - 需要验证测试脚本在 Docker 缺失时优雅降级\n436: \n437: ## Alternatives Considered\n438: \n439: ### 方案 1: 使用 Task (taskfile.dev) 替代 Make\n440: \n441: **优点:**\n442: - 更现代的语法，支持 YAML\n443: - 跨平台兼容性更好\n444: - 支持任务依赖和并行执行\n445: \n446: **缺点:**\n447: - 需要额外安装 Task 工具\n448: - 增加学习成本\n449: - Make 在项目中的使用已经很普遍\n450: \n451: **决策:** 继续使用 Makefile，保持简单和普遍兼容性。\n452: \n453: ### 方案 2: 使用 Shell 脚本替代 Makefile\n454: \n455: **优点:**\n456: - 更灵活，支持复杂逻辑\n457: - 无需学习 Make 语法\n458: \n459: **缺点:**\n460: - 缺少目标依赖管理\n461: - 并行执行能力弱\n462: - 不适合管理大量相关命令\n463: \n464: **决策:** Makefile 更适合管理构建目标体系。\n465: \n466: ### 方案 3: 每个组件独立 Makefile\n467: \n468: **优点:**\n469: - 组件解耦\n470: - 各自维护构建逻辑\n471: \n472: **缺点:**\n473: - 重复配置（变量、公共目标）\n474: - 全量构建需要多次调用\n475: - 增加维护成本\n476: \n477: **决策:** 使用根目录统一 Makefile，通过目标前缀区分组件。\n478: \n479: ### 方案 4: 完全依赖 CI/CD（本地无构建）\n480: \n481: **优点:**\n482: - 本地环境简化\n483: - 构建一致性高\n484: \n485: **缺点:**\n486: - 开发调试效率低\n487: - 依赖网络和服务可用性\n488: \n489: **决策:** 保留本地构建能力，CI/CD 作为补充。\n490: \n491: ## Testing Strategy\n492: \n493: ### Makefile 目标测试\n494: \n495: 1. **目标可用性测试** - 验证所有 `make` 目标可被调用\n496: 2. **依赖关系测试** - 验证目标依赖正确（如 `docker-build-all` 依赖各组件构建）\n497: 3. **变量覆盖测试** - 验证环境变量可正确覆盖默认值\n498: \n499: ### 脚本测试\n500: \n501: 1. **验证脚本测试** - 对合法镜像验证通过，对非法镜像验证失败\n502: 2. **构建测试** - 验证 Dockerfile、Docker daemon、buildx 检测有效\n503: 3. **运行时测试** - 验证容器启动、健康检查、端口检测有效\n504: \n505: ### 集成测试\n506: \n507: 1. **完整流程测试** - `make docker-build-all` → `make docker-validate` → `make kind-load-all`\n508: 2. **错误处理测试** - Docker 未运行时给出友好提示\n509: 3. **清理测试** - `make docker-clean` 正确清理镜像\n510: \n511: ### 测试覆盖目标\n512: \n513: - Makefile 目标：100%（所有目标可执行）\n514: - 验证脚本：100%（所有检查项有效）\n515: - 构建测试：100%（所有前置检查有效）\n516: - 运行时测试：100%（所有运行时检查有效）\n517: \n518: ## Acceptance Criteria\n519: \n520: - [ ] Makefile 所有目标可正常执行 (`make help` 列出所有目标)\n521: - [ ] `make docker-build-all` 成功构建三个镜像\n522: - [ ] `make docker-push-all` 成功推送镜像（需有推送权限）\n523: - [ ] `make kind-load-all` 成功加载镜像到 Kind 集群\n524: - [ ] `make docker-validate` 成功验证镜像\n525: - [ ] `make docker-test` 成功运行所有测试\n526: - [ ] `make docker-clean` 成功清理本地镜像\n527: - [ ] `make docker-buildx-all` 成功构建多架构镜像（需 buildx）\n528: - [ ] 验证脚本 (`validate.sh`) 可独立执行\n529: - [ ] 构建测试脚本 (`build_test.sh`) 可独立执行\n530: - [ ] 运行时测试脚本 (`runtime_test.sh`) 可独立执行\n531: - [ ] 所有脚本具有执行权限\n532: - [ ] 文档完整（帮助信息、使用说明）\n533: \n534: ## Dependencies\n535: \n536: ### 必需依赖\n537: - GNU Make ≥3.81\n538: - Docker ≥20.10\n539: - Bash ≥4.0\n540: - Git\n541: \n542: ### 可选依赖\n543: - Docker Buildx ≥0.6（多架构构建）\n544: - Kind ≥0.11（本地 Kubernetes 测试）\n545: \n546: ### 被依赖\n547: - AR-032 (Dockerfile 多阶段构建) - 提供 Dockerfile\n548: - AR-030 (Helm Chart) - 镜像用于 Helm 部署\n549: \n550: ## Migration Notes\n551: \n552: ### 从现有 Makefile 迁移\n553: \n554: 当前 Makefile 已经是最新状态，无需迁移。新增的脚本文件是 Makefile 目标的依赖，需要创建。\n555: \n556: ### 破坏性变更\n557: 无 - 仅补充缺失的脚本文件。\n558: \n559: ### 行为变更\n560: - `make docker-validate` 从失败变为成功（验证脚本存在后）\n561: - `make docker-test` 从失败变为成功（测试脚本存在后）\n562: \n563: ## Open Questions\n564: \n565: 1. 是否需要支持 Windows 环境下的 Makefile 等价物（如 PowerShell 脚本）？\n566: 2. 是否需要集成镜像签名（cosign）到 Makefile 目标？\n567: 3. 是否需要支持远程 Docker daemon（DOCKER_HOST 环境变量）？\n568: \n569: ## References\n570: \n571: - `Makefile` - 现有 Makefile 文件\n572: - `changes/AR-032/proposal.md` - Dockerfile 多阶段构建提案\n573: - `deployment/docker/Dockerfile` - Workload Manager Dockerfile\n574: - `deployment/docker/Dockerfile.router` - Router Dockerfile\n575: - `deployment/docker/Dockerfile.picod` - Picod Dockerfile\n576: - GNU Make Best Practices: https://www.gnu.org/software/make/manual/make.html\n577: - Docker Makefile Best Practices: https://docs.docker.com/build/building/best-practices/\n\n(End of file - total 577 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-033: Makefile 构建目标体系\n\n## Purpose\n\n本提案实现 AgentCube 项目的 Makefile 构建目标体系，为 Docker 镜像构建、推送、验证、测试提供标准化的自动化命令。该 Makefile 是 AgentCube 容器化工作流的核心入口，支撑开发、CI/CD、生产环境的镜像生命周期管理。\n\n目标是：\n\n1. **构建自动化** - 提供统一的 `make` 命令简化 Docker 镜像构建流程，减少手动操作错误\n2. **目标分层** - 支持全量构建 (`docker-build-all`) 和单组件构建 (`docker-build-workloadmanager` 等)，适应不同场景\n3. **推送标准化** - 统一镜像推送流程，自动关联 VERSION、COMMIT_SHA、DOCKER_TAG 多标签\n4. **集群集成** - 提供 Kind 集群加载目标 (`kind-load-all`)，支持本地开发测试\n5. **多架构支持** - 集成 Docker Buildx，支持 amd64、arm64 多架构镜像构建\n6. **质量门禁** - 内置镜像验证 (`docker-validate`) 和测试 (`docker-test`) 目标，确保镜像质量\n7. **清理工具** - 提供本地镜像清理目标 (`docker-clean`)，减少磁盘占用\n\n本提案基于 existing Makefile (仅包含 Docker 相关目标) 进行扩展，遵循 Makefile 最佳实践和 AR-032 Dockerfile 多阶段构建规范。\n\n## Scope\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-033/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775882863950,"end":1775882864013}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882864017,"sessionID":"ses_285222e43ffe4HfnmS1LBKuzWs","part":{"id":"prt_d7addf869001nSBsYvqk4rxFSj","messageID":"msg_d7adde8460013byXPzCH6uxzwV","sessionID":"ses_285222e43ffe4HfnmS1LBKuzWs","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_da1e297c7d464b859ec33171","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-032/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-032/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-032: Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images)\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: 本提案实现 AgentCube 项目的 Dockerfile 多阶段构建，为 Workload Manager、Router、Volcano Agent Scheduler 三个核心组件提供独立的容器镜像构建能力。该 Dockerfile 是 AgentCube 控制平面组件容器化的基础，支撑 Helm Chart 部署和 Kubernetes 运行时环境。\n6: \n7: 目标是：\n8: \n9: 1. **多阶段构建优化** - 使用多阶段构建减少最终镜像体积，仅包含运行必需的二进制文件和配置\n10: 2. **三镜像分离** - 为 Workload Manager、Router、Volcano Agent Scheduler 分别构建独立镜像，支持差异化部署\n11: 3. **最小化攻击面** - 基于 distroless 或 alpine 基础镜像，减少安全漏洞风险\n12: 4. **构建可复用** - 统一的 Dockerfile 模板支持本地构建、CI/CD 流水线、多架构支持\n13: 5. **环境一致性** - 确保开发、测试、生产环境的镜像构建行为一致\n14: 6. **版本可追溯** - 镜像标签与 Git commit/Tag 关联，支持版本追踪和回滚\n15: \n16: 本提案基于 deployment/design.md 和 deployment/spec.md 的规范，遵循 Docker 多阶段构建最佳实践。\n17: \n18: ## Scope\n19: \n20: **Module:** docker  \n21: **Language:** Dockerfile  \n22: **Size:** S\n23: \n24: 本 AR 包含：\n25: \n26: - **包含内容：**\n27:   - Dockerfile.workloadmanager - Workload Manager 镜像构建\n28:   - Dockerfile.router - Router 镜像构建\n29:   - Dockerfile.volcano-agent-scheduler - Volcano Agent Scheduler 镜像构建\n30:   - .dockerignore 文件 - 构建上下文忽略规则\n31:   - Makefile 构建目标 - 简化镜像构建命令\n32:   - 镜像验证脚本 - 验证镜像大小、层数、安全性\n33:   - 构建文档和使用示例\n34: \n35: - **不包含内容：**\n36:   - Helm Chart 模板（由 AR-030 管理）\n37:   - Kubernetes 部署配置\n38:   - CI/CD 流水线配置\n39:   - 镜像仓库推送逻辑\n40: \n41: ## Current State Analysis\n42: \n43: ### 现有构建状态\n44: \n45: 根据项目结构 `cmd/` 目录：\n46: - `cmd/agentcube/` - Workload Manager 源码（Go）\n47: - `cmd/agentcube-admin/` - 管理工具（Go）\n48: - `cmd/agentcube-proxy/` - 代理服务（Go）\n49: - `cmd/agentcube-shell/` - Shell 工具（Go）\n50: - `cmd/agentd/` - Agent Daemon（Go，已有二进制文件）\n51: - `cmd/cli/` - CLI 工具（Python）\n52: \n53: 当前无 Dockerfile，缺少容器化构建能力。\n54: \n55: ### 参考设计规范\n56: \n57: 根据 `deployment/design.md` 和 `deployment/spec.md`：\n58: \n59: **镜像要求：**\n60: - Workload Manager: 基于 Go 二进制文件，暴露 8080 端口\n61: - Router: 基于 Go 二进制文件，暴露 8080 端口\n62: - Volcano Agent Scheduler: 基于 Go 二进制文件，暴露 8080 端口（metrics）\n63: \n64: **基础镜像要求：**\n65: - 生产镜像：使用 gcr.io/distroless/static-debian11 或 alpine:3.18\n66: - 构建镜像：使用 golang:1.21-bookworm\n67: \n68: **镜像标签规范：**\n69: - latest - 最新开发版本\n70: - <version> - 语义化版本（如 0.1.0）\n71: - <commit-sha> - Git commit SHA\n72: \n73: ### 差距分析\n74: \n75: 1. **缺少 Dockerfile** - 无任何 Dockerfile，无法构建容器镜像\n76: 2. **缺少构建优化** - 未使用多阶段构建，镜像体积可能过大\n77: 3. **缺少安全加固** - 未使用 distroless 或最小化基础镜像\n78: 4. **缺少构建自动化** - 无 Makefile 构建目标或脚本\n79: \n80: ### deployment/spec.md 关键要求\n81: \n82: 1. **镜像分离** - 每个组件独立镜像，避免耦合\n83: 2. **端口暴露** - Workload Manager 8080, Router 8080, Scheduler 8080 (metrics)\n84: 3. **环境变量** - 支持 REDIS_ADDR, REDIS_PASSWORD, AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE 等\n85: 4. **健康检查** - Docker HEALTHCHECK 指令配置\n86: 5. **非 root 用户** - 生产镜像以非 root 用户运行\n87: \n88: ## Proposed Changes\n89: \n90: ### 1. 目录结构\n91: \n92: ```\n93: docker/\n94: ├── .dockerignore                       # 构建上下文忽略\n95: ├── Dockerfile.workloadmanager          # Workload Manager Dockerfile\n96: ├── Dockerfile.router                   # Router Dockerfile\n97: ├── Dockerfile.volcano-agent-scheduler  # Volcano Agent Scheduler Dockerfile\n98: ├── Makefile                            # 构建目标\n99: ├── validate.sh                         # 镜像验证脚本\n100: └── README.md                           # 构建说明文档\n101: ```\n102: \n103: ### 2. .dockerignore\n104: \n105: ```dockerignore\n106: # .dockerignore\n107: # Build context ignores\n108: \n109: # Git\n110: .git\n111: .gitignore\n112: \n113: # Build artifacts\n114: bin/\n115: dist/\n116: *.out\n117: \n118: # Dependencies\n119: vendor/\n120: \n121: # IDE\n122: .idea/\n123: .vscode/\n124: *.swp\n125: *.swo\n126: \n127: # Documentation\n128: *.md\n129: !README.md\n130: \n131: # Tests\n132: testing/\n133: *_test.go\n134: \n135: # Docker\n136: docker/\n137: Dockerfile*\n138: \n139: # Helm\n140: manifests/\n141: \n142: # Python\n143: __pycache__/\n144: *.pyc\n145: .pytest_cache/\n146: \n147: # Misc\n148: .DS_Store\n149: Thumbs.db\n150: ```\n151: \n152: ### 3. Workload Manager Dockerfile\n153: \n154: ```dockerfile\n155: # docker/Dockerfile.workloadmanager\n156: # Multi-stage build for Workload Manager\n157: \n158: # Stage 1: Build\n159: FROM golang:1.21-bookworm AS builder\n160: \n161: WORKDIR /build\n162: \n163: # Copy go mod files\n164: COPY go.mod go.sum ./\n165: RUN go mod download\n166: \n167: # Copy source code\n168: COPY cmd/agentcube ./cmd/agentcube\n169: COPY pkg ./pkg\n170: \n171: # Build the binary\n172: RUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux GOARCH=amd64 go build \\\n173:     -ldflags=\"-w -s\" \\\n174:     -o /build/workloadmanager \\\n175:     ./cmd/agentcube\n176: \n177: # Stage 2: Runtime (distroless)\n178: FROM gcr.io/distroless/static-debian11:nonroot AS runtime\n179: \n180: # Copy binary from builder\n181: COPY --from=builder /build/workloadmanager /workloadmanager\n182: \n183: # Set non-root user\n184: USER nonroot:nonroot\n185: \n186: # Set working directory\n187: WORKDIR /\n188: \n189: # Expose port\n190: EXPOSE 8080\n191: \n192: # Health check\n193: HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \\\n194:     CMD [\"/workloadmanager\", \"--health\"]\n195: \n196: # Entrypoint\n197: ENTRYPOINT [\"/workloadmanager\"]\n198: CMD [\"--port=8080\"]\n199: ```\n200: \n201: ### 4. Router Dockerfile\n202: \n203: ```dockerfile\n204: # docker/Dockerfile.router\n205: # Multi-stage build for Router\n206: \n207: # Stage 1: Build\n208: FROM golang:1.21-bookworm AS builder\n209: \n210: WORKDIR /build\n211: \n212: # Copy go mod files\n213: COPY go.mod go.sum ./\n214: RUN go mod download\n215: \n216: # Copy source code\n217: COPY cmd/agentcube-proxy ./cmd/agentcube-proxy\n218: COPY pkg ./pkg\n219: \n220: # Build the binary\n221: RUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux GOARCH=amd64 go build \\\n222:     -ldflags=\"-w -s\" \\\n223:     -o /build/router \\\n224:     ./cmd/agentcube-proxy\n225: \n226: # Stage 2: Runtime (distroless)\n227: FROM gcr.io/distroless/static-debian11:nonroot AS runtime\n228: \n229: # Copy binary from builder\n230: COPY --from=builder /build/router /router\n231: \n232: # Set non-root user\n233: USER nonroot:nonroot\n234: \n235: # Set working directory\n236: WORKDIR /\n237: \n238: # Expose port\n239: EXPOSE 8080\n240: \n241: # Health check\n242: HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \\\n243:     CMD [\"/router\", \"--health\"]\n244: \n245: # Entrypoint\n246: ENTRYPOINT [\"/router\"]\n247: CMD [\"--port=8080\", \"--debug\"]\n248: ```\n249: \n250: ### 5. Volcano Agent Scheduler Dockerfile\n251: \n252: ```dockerfile\n253: # docker/Dockerfile.volcano-agent-scheduler\n254: # Multi-stage build for Volcano Agent Scheduler\n255: \n256: # Stage 1: Build\n257: FROM golang:1.21-bookworm AS builder\n258: \n259: WORKDIR /build\n260: \n261: # Copy go mod files\n262: COPY go.mod go.sum ./\n263: RUN go mod download\n264: \n265: # Copy source code\n266: COPY cmd/agentd ./cmd/agentd\n267: COPY pkg ./pkg\n268: \n269: # Build the binary\n270: RUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux GOARCH=amd64 go build \\\n271:     -ldflags=\"-w -s\" \\\n272:     -o /build/volcano-agent-scheduler \\\n273:     ./cmd/agentd\n274: \n275: # Stage 2: Runtime (distroless)\n276: FROM gcr.io/distroless/static-debian11:nonroot AS runtime\n277: \n278: # Copy binary from builder\n279: COPY --from=builder /build/volcano-agent-scheduler /volcano-agent-scheduler\n280: \n281: # Copy default config\n282: COPY sandbox-orchestration/agent-scheduler.conf /config/agent-scheduler.conf\n283: \n284: # Set non-root user\n285: USER nonroot:nonroot\n286: \n287: # Set working directory\n288: WORKDIR /\n289: \n290: # Expose metrics port\n291: EXPOSE 8080\n292: \n293: # Health check\n294: HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \\\n295:     CMD [\"/volcano-agent-scheduler\", \"--health\"]\n296: \n297: # Entrypoint\n298: ENTRYPOINT [\"/volcano-agent-scheduler\"]\n299: CMD [\"--scheduler-name=agent-scheduler\", \"--config=/config/agent-scheduler.conf\"]\n300: ```\n301: \n302: ### 6. Makefile Build Targets\n303: \n304: ```makefile\n305: # Makefile (add to root or docker/Makefile)\n306: \n307: # Docker build configuration\n308: DOCKER_REGISTRY ?= ghcr.io/volcano-sh\n309: DOCKER_TAG ?= latest\n310: VERSION ?= $(shell git describe --tags --always --dirty)\n311: COMMIT_SHA ?= $(shell git rev-parse --short HEAD)\n312: \n313: # Image names\n314: WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE := $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/workloadmanager\n315: ROUTER_IMAGE := $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/agentcube-router\n316: VOLCANO_SCHEDULER_IMAGE := $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/vc-agent-scheduler\n317: \n318: # Build targets\n319: .PHONY: docker-build\n320: docker-build: docker-build-workloadmanager docker-build-router docker-build-scheduler\n321: \n322: .PHONY: docker-build-workloadmanager\n323: docker-build-workloadmanager:\n324: \tdocker build \\\n325: \t\t-f docker/Dockerfile.workloadmanager \\\n326: \t\t-t $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) \\\n327: \t\t-t $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n328: \t\t.\n329: \n330: .PHONY: docker-build-router\n331: docker-build-router:\n332: \tdocker build \\\n333: \t\t-f docker/Dockerfile.router \\\n334: \t\t-t $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) \\\n335: \t\t-t $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n336: \t\t.\n337: \n338: .PHONY: docker-build-scheduler\n339: docker-build-scheduler:\n340: \tdocker build \\\n341: \t\t-f docker/Dockerfile.volcano-agent-scheduler \\\n342: \t\t-t $(VOLCANO_SCHEDULER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) \\\n343: \t\t-t $(VOLCANO_SCHEDULER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n344: \t\t.\n345: \n346: .PHONY: docker-push\n347: docker-push: docker-push-workloadmanager docker-push-router docker-push-scheduler\n348: \n349: .PHONY: docker-push-workloadmanager\n350: docker-push-workloadmanager:\n351: \tdocker push $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n352: \tdocker push $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA)\n353: \n354: .PHONY: docker-push-router\n355: docker-push-router:\n356: \tdocker push $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n357: \tdocker push $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA)\n358: \n359: .PHONY: docker-push-scheduler\n360: docker-push-scheduler:\n361: \tdocker push $(VOLCANO_SCHEDULER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n362: \tdocker push $(VOLCANO_SCHEDULER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA)\n363: \n364: .PHONY: docker-validate\n365: docker-validate:\n366: \t./docker/validate.sh\n367: \n368: .PHONY: docker-clean\n369: docker-clean:\n370: \tdocker rmi $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) 2>/dev/null || true\n371: \tdocker rmi $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) 2>/dev/null || true\n372: \tdocker rmi $(VOLCANO_SCHEDULER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) 2>/dev/null || true\n373: ```\n374: \n375: ### 7. 镜像验证脚本\n376: \n377: ```bash\n378: #!/bin/bash\n379: # docker/validate.sh\n380: \n381: set -e\n382: \n383: WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE=\"${DOCKER_REGISTRY:-ghcr.io/volcano-sh}/workloadmanager:${DOCKER_TAG:-latest}\"\n384: ROUTER_IMAGE=\"${DOCKER_REGISTRY:-ghcr.io/volcano-sh}/agentcube-router:${DOCKER_TAG:-latest}\"\n385: VOLCANO_SCHEDULER_IMAGE=\"${DOCKER_REGISTRY:-ghcr.io/volcano-sh}/vc-agent-scheduler:${DOCKER_TAG:-latest}\"\n386: \n387: echo \"Validating Docker images...\"\n388: echo \"\"\n389: \n390: # Function to check image\n391: check_image() {\n392:     local image=$1\n393:     local name=$2\n394:     \n395:     echo \"Checking $name...\"\n396:     \n397:     # Check if image exists\n398:     if ! docker image inspect \"$image\" > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n399:         echo \"  ✗ Image not found: $image\"\n400:         return 1\n401:     fi\n402:     echo \"  ✓ Image exists\"\n403:     \n404:     # Check image size (should be < 50MB for distroless)\n405:     local size=$(docker image inspect \"$image\" --format='{{.Size}}')\n406:     local size_mb=$((size / 1024 / 1024))\n407:     if [ $size_mb -lt 50 ]; then\n408:         echo \"  ✓ Image size: ${size_mb}MB (< 50MB)\"\n409:     else\n410:         echo \"  ✗ Image size: ${size_mb}MB (>= 50MB)\"\n411:         return 1\n412:     fi\n413:     \n414:     # Check layer count (should be <= 5)\n415:     local layers=$(docker image history \"$image\" --format='{{.ID}}' | wc -l)\n416:     if [ $layers -le 5 ]; then\n417:         echo \"  ✓ Layer count: $layers (<= 5)\"\n418:     else\n419:         echo \"  ✗ Layer count: $layers (> 5)\"\n420:         return 1\n421:     fi\n422:     \n423:     # Check if running as non-root\n424:     local user=$(docker image inspect \"$image\" --format='{{.Config.User}}')\n425:     if [ -n \"$user\" ] && [ \"$user\" != \"root\" ]; then\n426:         echo \"  ✓ Running as non-root: $user\"\n427:     else\n428:         echo \"  ✗ Running as root or no user specified\"\n429:         return 1\n430:     fi\n431:     \n432:     # Check exposed ports\n433:     local ports=$(docker image inspect \"$image\" --format='{{json .Config.ExposedPorts}}')\n434:     if echo \"$ports\" | grep -q \"8080\"; then\n435:         echo \"  ✓ Port 8080 exposed\"\n436:     else\n437:         echo \"  ✗ Port 8080 not exposed\"\n438:         return 1\n439:     fi\n440:     \n441:     # Check health check\n442:     local healthcheck=$(docker image inspect \"$image\" --format='{{json .Config.Healthcheck}}')\n443:     if [ \"$healthcheck\" != \"null\" ] && [ -n \"$healthcheck\" ]; then\n444:         echo \"  ✓ Health check configured\"\n445:     else\n446:         echo \"  ✗ Health check not configured\"\n447:         return 1\n448:     fi\n449:     \n450:     echo \"\"\n451: }\n452: \n453: # Validate all images\n454: check_image \"$WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE\" \"Workload Manager\"\n455: check_image \"$ROUTER_IMAGE\" \"Router\"\n456: check_image \"$VOLCANO_SCHEDULER_IMAGE\" \"Volcano Agent Scheduler\"\n457: \n458: echo \"All validations passed!\"\n459: ```\n460: \n461: ### 8. 构建文档 (docker/README.md)\n462: \n463: ```markdown\n464: # Docker Image Builds\n465: \n466: AgentCube 控制平面组件的 Docker 镜像构建配置。\n467: \n468: ## 镜像列表\n469: \n470: | 组件 | 镜像名 | 端口 | 大小目标 |\n471: |------|--------|------|----------|\n472: | Workload Manager | ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager | 8080 | < 50MB |\n473: | Router | ghcr.io/volcano-sh/agentcube-router | 8080 | < 50MB |\n474: | Volcano Agent Scheduler | ghcr.io/volcano-sh/vc-agent-scheduler | 8080 | < 50MB |\n475: \n476: ## 快速开始\n477: \n478: ### 构建所有镜像\n479: \n480: ```bash\n481: make docker-build\n482: ```\n483: \n484: ### 构建单个镜像\n485: \n486: ```bash\n487: make docker-build-workloadmanager\n488: make docker-build-router\n489: make docker-build-scheduler\n490: ```\n491: \n492: ### 推送镜像\n493: \n494: ```bash\n495: make docker-push\n496: ```\n497: \n498: ### 验证镜像\n499: \n500: ```bash\n501: make docker-validate\n502: ```\n503: \n504: ## 自定义配置\n505: \n506: ### 修改镜像仓库\n507: \n508: ```bash\n509: export DOCKER_REGISTRY=myregistry.com\n510: make docker-build\n511: ```\n512: \n513: ### 修改镜像标签\n514: \n515: ```bash\n516: export DOCKER_TAG=v0.1.0\n517: make docker-build\n518: ```\n519: \n520: ## 多架构支持\n521: \n522: ```bash\n523: docker buildx build \\\n524:   --platform linux/amd64,linux/arm64 \\\n525:   -t ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager:latest \\\n526:   --push \\\n527:   -f docker/Dockerfile.workloadmanager \\\n528:   .\n529: ```\n530: \n531: ## 安全最佳实践\n532: \n533: 1. **非 root 用户** - 所有镜像以 nonroot 用户运行\n534: 2. **Distroless 基础** - 使用 distroless/static-debian11 减少攻击面\n535: 3. **多阶段构建** - 仅复制必需的二进制文件\n536: 4. **静态链接** - CGO_ENABLED=0 避免动态库依赖\n537: 5. **健康检查** - 配置 HEALTHCHECK 指令\n538: \n539: ## 故障排查\n540: \n541: ### 镜像构建失败\n542: \n543: 检查 Go 代码是否能编译：\n544: ```bash\n545: go build -o /tmp/test ./cmd/agentcube\n546: ```\n547: \n548: ### 镜像过大\n549: \n550: 检查是否包含了不必要的文件：\n551: ```bash\n552: docker history <image-name>\n553: ```\n554: \n555: ### 权限错误\n556: \n557: 确保 Docker daemon 正常运行：\n558: ```bash\n559: docker info\n560: ```\n561: ```\n562: \n563: ## Impact Analysis\n564: \n565: ### 依赖影响\n566: \n567: | 依赖项 | 版本 | 用途 |\n568: |--------|------|------|\n569: | Docker | ≥20.10 | 镜像构建 |\n570: | Go | ≥1.21 | 应用编译 |\n571: | Make | 任意 | 构建自动化 |\n572: \n573: ### 模块依赖关系\n574: \n575: ```\n576: docker/\n577: ├── .dockerignore                       # 无依赖\n578: ├── Dockerfile.workloadmanager          # 依赖 cmd/agentcube, pkg/\n579: ├── Dockerfile.router                   # 依赖 cmd/agentcube-proxy, pkg/\n580: ├── Dockerfile.volcano-agent-scheduler  # 依赖 cmd/agentd, pkg/\n581: ├── Makefile                            # 依赖所有 Dockerfile\n582: ├── validate.sh                         # 依赖 docker CLI\n583: └── README.md                           # 文档\n584: ```\n585: \n586: ### 向后兼容性\n587: \n588: - 首次实现，无破坏性变更风险\n589: - 镜像标签策略支持版本追溯\n590: - 多架构支持未来扩展\n591: \n592: ### 测试影响\n593: \n594: - 需要验证镜像构建成功\n595: - 需要验证镜像大小符合目标\n596: - 需要验证容器可正常启动\n597: - 需要验证健康检查有效\n598: \n599: ## Alternatives Considered\n600: \n601: ### 方案 1: 单 Dockerfile 多目标构建\n602: \n603: **优点:**\n604: - 单一文件，易于维护\n605: - 使用 BUILDKIT 多目标\n606: \n607: **缺点:**\n608: - 文件过大，难以阅读\n609: - 不便于独立构建\n610: \n611: **决策:** 采用独立 Dockerfile，每个组件一个文件。\n612: \n613: ### 方案 2: 使用 Alpine 基础镜像\n614: \n615: **优点:**\n616: - 镜像体积小\n617: - 包管理方便\n618: \n619: **缺点:**\n620: - 存在已知安全漏洞\n621: - glibc 兼容性问题\n622: \n623: **决策:** 采用 distroless/static-debian11，更安全。\n624: \n625: ### 方案 3: 单一巨型镜像（包含所有组件）\n626: \n627: **优点:**\n628: - 单一镜像，部署简单\n629: - 减少镜像数量\n630: \n631: **缺点:**\n632: - 镜像体积大\n633: - 安全风险高\n634: - 无法独立部署组件\n635: \n636: **决策:** 采用独立镜像，支持最小化部署。\n637: \n638: ### 方案 4: 使用 Buildpacks\n639: \n640: **优点:**\n641: - 自动化程度高\n642: - 无需 Dockerfile\n643: \n644: **缺点:**\n645: - 定制化能力弱\n646: - 无法精确控制镜像内容\n647: \n648: **决策:** 采用 Dockerfile，保持完全控制。\n649: \n650: ## Testing Strategy\n651: \n652: ### 构建测试\n653: \n654: 1. **本地构建测试** - 验证所有 Dockerfile 可成功构建\n655: 2. **镜像大小测试** - 验证镜像体积 < 50MB\n656: 3. **层数测试** - 验证镜像层数 <= 5\n657: \n658: ### 功能测试\n659: \n660: 1. **容器启动测试** - 验证容器可正常启动\n661: 2. **健康检查测试** - 验证 HEALTHCHECK 有效\n662: 3. **端口暴露测试** - 验证 8080 端口可访问\n663: \n664: ### 安全测试\n665: \n666: 1. **非 root 测试** - 验证容器以非 root 用户运行\n667: 2. **漏洞扫描** - 使用 Trivy 扫描镜像漏洞\n668: 3. **最小权限测试** - 验证容器无多余权限\n669: \n670: ### 测试覆盖目标\n671: \n672: - Dockerfile: 100%（所有指令正确）\n673: - 构建脚本：100%（所有目标有效）\n674: - 验证脚本：100%（所有检查项通过）\n675: \n676: ## Acceptance Criteria\n677: \n678: - [ ] Workload Manager Dockerfile 可成功构建\n679: - [ ] Router Dockerfile 可成功构建\n680: - [ ] Volcano Agent Scheduler Dockerfile 可成功构建\n681: - [ ] 镜像大小 < 50MB\n682: - [ ] 镜像层数 <= 5\n683: - [ ] 容器以非 root 用户运行\n684: - [ ] 健康检查配置正确\n685: - [ ] 端口 8080 暴露\n686: - [ ] Makefile 构建目标可用\n687: - [ ] 验证脚本通过所有检查\n688: - [ ] 文档完整（构建说明、故障排查）\n689: \n690: ## Dependencies\n691: \n692: ### 必需依赖\n693: - Docker ≥20.10\n694: - Go ≥1.21\n695: - Make\n696: \n697: ### 可选依赖\n698: - Docker Buildx（多架构支持）\n699: - Trivy（安全扫描）\n700: \n701: ### 被依赖\n702: - AR-030 (Helm Chart) - 镜像用于 Helm Chart 部署\n703: - cmd/agentcube, cmd/agentcube-proxy, cmd/agentd - 应用源码\n704: \n705: ## Migration Notes\n706: \n707: ### 从手动构建迁移\n708: \n709: 1. 安装 Docker 和 Go 1.21+\n710: 2. 运行 `make docker-build` 构建镜像\n711: 3. 验证镜像 `make docker-validate`\n712: 4. 更新 Helm values.yaml 使用新镜像\n713: \n714: ### 破坏性变更\n715: 无 - 首次实现。\n716: \n717: ### 行为变更\n718: - 从源码编译改为容器化部署\n719: - 从直接运行改为容器运行\n720: \n721: ## Open Questions\n722: \n723: 1. 是否需要支持 Windows 容器？（未来扩展）\n724: 2. 是否需要集成镜像签名？（待需求明确）\n725: 3. 是否需要支持自定义基础镜像？（待需求明确）\n726: \n727: ## References\n728: \n729: - `deployment/spec.md` - 部署规范\n730: - `deployment/design.md` - 部署设计\n731: - `cmd/agentcube/` - Workload Manager 源码\n732: - `cmd/agentcube-proxy/` - Router 源码\n733: - `cmd/agentd/` - Volcano Agent Scheduler 源码\n734: - Docker Best Practices: https://docs.docker.com/develop/develop-images/dockerfile_best-practices/\n735: - Distroless Images: https://github.com/GoogleContainerTools/distroless\n\n(End of file - total 735 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-032: Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images)\n\n## Purpose\n\n本提案实现 AgentCube 项目的 Dockerfile 多阶段构建，为 Workload Manager、Router、Volcano Agent Scheduler 三个核心组件提供独立的容器镜像构建能力。该 Dockerfile 是 AgentCube 控制平面组件容器化的基础，支撑 Helm Chart 部署和 Kubernetes 运行时环境。\n\n目标是：\n\n1. **多阶段构建优化** - 使用多阶段构建减少最终镜像体积，仅包含运行必需的二进制文件和配置\n2. **三镜像分离** - 为 Workload Manager、Router、Volcano Agent Scheduler 分别构建独立镜像，支持差异化部署\n3. **最小化攻击面** - 基于 distroless 或 alpine 基础镜像，减少安全漏洞风险\n4. **构建可复用** - 统一的 Dockerfile 模板支持本地构建、CI/CD 流水线、多架构支持\n5. **环境一致性** - 确保开发、测试、生产环境的镜像构建行为一致\n6. **版本可追溯** - 镜像标签与 Git commit/Tag 关联，支持版本追踪和回滚\n\n本提案基于 deployment/design.md 和 deployment/spec.md 的规范，遵循 Docker 多阶段构建最佳实践。\n\n## Scope\n\n**Module:** docker  ","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-032/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775882863954,"end":1775882864015}}}}
