{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775883070534,"sessionID":"ses_285222e43ffe4HfnmS1LBKuzWs","part":{"id":"prt_d7ade2c87001hDa66iCLmK9azJ","messageID":"msg_d7ade22ba001hB2NwaeN98VZgv","sessionID":"ses_285222e43ffe4HfnmS1LBKuzWs","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_ef33dfdbfb7a41a7b3046437","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-034/proposal.md","content":"# AR-034: CI/CD GitHub Actions (12 workflows)\n\n## Purpose\n\n本提案实现 AgentCube 项目的 GitHub Actions CI/CD 流水线体系，为代码质量、构建验证、镜像发布、安全扫描提供自动化流水线。该 CI/CD 体系是 AgentCube 工程化实践的核心基础设施，支撑持续集成、持续交付、质量门禁全流程。\n\n目标是：\n\n1. **代码质量门禁** - 在 PR 和 push 事件中自动运行 lint、typecheck、test，确保代码质量\n2. **构建验证** - 验证 Go 和 Python 代码可编译，Docker 镜像可构建\n3. **多架构支持** - 构建 amd64、arm64 多架构 Docker 镜像，支持异构集群\n4. **镜像发布** - 自动推送镜像到 GHCR，支持版本标签管理（latest, commit-sha, semver）\n5. **安全扫描** - 集成 Trivy 扫描镜像漏洞，集成 CodeQL 扫描代码安全问题\n6. **文档站点** - 自动构建和部署 Docusaurus 文档到 GitHub Pages\n7. **发布自动化** - 创建 GitHub Release，生成变更日志，上传构建产物\n8. **依赖更新** - 自动检测依赖更新，创建 Dependabot PR\n\n本提案基于 AR-032（Dockerfile 多阶段构建）、AR-033（Makefile 构建目标）实现，遵循 GitHub Actions 最佳实践和 AgentCube 工程规范。\n\n## Scope\n\n**Module:** .github  \n**Language:** YAML  \n**Size:** L\n\n本 AR 包含：\n\n- **包含内容：**\n  - `.github/workflows/ci.yml` - CI 流水线（lint, test, build）\n  - `.github/workflows/cd.yml` - CD 流水线（镜像推送、发布）\n  - `.github/workflows/security-scan.yml` - 安全扫描（Trivy, CodeQL）\n  - `.github/workflows/docs.yml` - 文档构建和部署\n  - `.github/workflows/multi-arch-build.yml` - 多架构镜像构建\n  - `.github/workflows/e2e-test.yml` - 端到端测试\n  - `.github/workflows/nightly-build.yml` - 夜间构建\n  - `.github/workflows/pr-validation.yml` - PR 验证\n  - `.github/workflows/release.yml` - Release 发布\n  - `.github/workflows/dependency-review.yml` - 依赖审查\n  - `.github/workflows/stale.yml` -  stale 管理\n  - `.github/workflows/labeler.yml` - 自动标签\n  - `.github/dependabot.yml` - Dependabot 配置\n  - `.github/labeler.yml` - 自动标签规则\n  - `.github/CODEOWNERS` - 代码所有者\n  - 相关 Action 配置和脚本\n\n- **不包含内容：**\n  - Dockerfile 编写（由 AR-032 管理）\n  - Makefile 编写（由 AR-033 管理）\n  - Helm Chart 打包发布（由 AR-030 管理）\n  - 文档内容编写（由文档团队管理）\n\n## Current State Analysis\n\n### 现有 CI/CD 状态\n\n根据项目结构检查：\n- 无 `.github/workflows/` 目录\n- 无 `.github/dependabot.yml`\n- 无 `.github/CODEOWNERS`\n- 无现有 GitHub Actions 配置\n\n### 参考设计规范\n\n根据 `project.md` 和 AR-032、AR-033：\n\n**技术栈要求：**\n- Go 1.24 - 需要配置 Go 环境\n- Python ≥3.10 - 需要配置 Python 环境\n- Docker - 需要 Docker in Docker 或 Runner 预装\n- Helm 3 - 需要 Helm 工具\n- Kubernetes - 需要 Kind 或 K3s 进行测试\n\n**镜像仓库：**\n- GHCR (ghcr.io/volcano-sh) - GitHub Container Registry\n- 标签策略：latest, <commit-sha>, <version>\n\n**发布流程：**\n- Git tag 触发 Release\n- 语义化版本：vMajor.Minor.Patch\n- 自动生成交付物\n\n### 差距分析\n\n1. **缺少工作流文件** - 无任何 GitHub Actions 工作流\n2. **缺少依赖管理** - 无 Dependabot 配置\n3. **缺少代码所有者** - 无 CODEOWNERS 配置\n4. **缺少标签管理** - 无自动标签规则\n5. **缺少安全策略** - 无安全扫描配置\n\n### 项目特殊需求\n\n根据 AgentCube 架构：\n\n1. **Kubernetes 测试** - 需要 Kind 集群测试 K8s 集成\n2. **Redis 测试** - 需要 Redis 服务测试缓存层\n3. **多组件构建** - Workload Manager、Router、Volcano Agent Scheduler 三个组件\n4. **Python SDK/CLI** - 需要 Python 包构建和发布\n5. **Helm Chart** - 需要 Helm lint 和打包\n6. **文档站点** - Docusaurus 构建和部署\n\n## Proposed Changes\n\n### 1. 目录结构\n\n```\n.github/\n├── workflows/\n│   ├── ci.yml                      # CI 主流水线\n│   ├── cd.yml                      # CD 发布流水线\n│   ├── security-scan.yml           # 安全扫描\n│   ├── docs.yml                    # 文档部署\n│   ├── multi-arch-build.yml        # 多架构构建\n│   ├── e2e-test.yml                # 端到端测试\n│   ├── nightly-build.yml           # 夜间构建\n│   ├── pr-validation.yml           # PR 验证\n│   ├── release.yml                 # Release 发布\n│   ├── dependency-review.yml       # 依赖审查\n│   ├── stale.yml                   # Stale 管理\n│   └── labeler.yml                 # 自动标签\n├── dependabot.yml                  # Dependabot 配置\n├── labeler.yml                     # 标签规则\n└── CODEOWNERS                      # 代码所有者\n```\n\n### 2. CI 主流水线 (ci.yml)\n\n```yaml\n# .github/workflows/ci.yml\nname: CI\n\non:\n  push:\n    branches: [main, develop]\n  pull_request:\n    branches: [main, develop]\n\nenv:\n  GO_VERSION: '1.24'\n  PYTHON_VERSION: '3.11'\n  NODE_VERSION: '20'\n\npermissions:\n  contents: read\n\njobs:\n  go-lint:\n    name: Go Lint\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Setup Go\n        uses: actions/setup-go@v5\n        with:\n          go-version: ${{ env.GO_VERSION }}\n          cache: true\n\n      - name: Run golangci-lint\n        uses: golangci/golangci-lint-action@v6\n        with:\n          version: latest\n          args: --timeout=5m\n\n  go-test:\n    name: Go Test\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    services:\n      redis:\n        image: redis:7-alpine\n        ports:\n          - 6379:6379\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Setup Go\n        uses: actions/setup-go@v5\n        with:\n          go-version: ${{ env.GO_VERSION }}\n          cache: true\n\n      - name: Run tests\n        run: go test -race -coverprofile=coverage.out ./...\n\n      - name: Upload coverage\n        uses: codecov/codecov-action@v4\n        with:\n          file: ./coverage.out\n          flags: go\n\n  python-lint:\n    name: Python Lint\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Setup Python\n        uses: actions/setup-python@v5\n        with:\n          python-version: ${{ env.PYTHON_VERSION }}\n\n      - name: Install dependencies\n        run: |\n          pip install ruff mypy\n          pip install -e sdk-python/\n\n      - name: Run ruff\n        run: ruff check sdk-python/ cmd/cli/\n\n      - name: Run mypy\n        run: mypy sdk-python/ cmd/cli/\n\n  python-test:\n    name: Python Test\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    services:\n      redis:\n        image: redis:7-alpine\n        ports:\n          - 6379:6379\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Setup Python\n        uses: actions/setup-python@v5\n        with:\n          python-version: ${{ env.PYTHON_VERSION }}\n\n      - name: Install dependencies\n        run: |\n          pip install pytest pytest-cov\n          pip install -e sdk-python/\n\n      - name: Run tests\n        run: pytest --cov=sdk-python sdk-python/ tests/\n\n      - name: Upload coverage\n        uses: codecov/codecov-action@v4\n        with:\n          file: ./coverage.xml\n          flags: python\n\n  helm-lint:\n    name: Helm Lint\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Setup Helm\n        uses: azure/setup-helm@v3\n        with:\n          version: v3.14.0\n\n      - name: Run helm lint\n        run: helm lint manifests/\n\n  build-verify:\n    name: Build Verify\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    needs: [go-lint, go-test, python-lint, python-test]\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Setup Go\n        uses: actions/setup-go@v5\n        with:\n          go-version: ${{ env.GO_VERSION }}\n\n      - name: Build Go binaries\n        run: |\n          go build -o /tmp/workloadmanager ./cmd/agentcube\n          go build -o /tmp/router ./cmd/agentcube-proxy\n          go build -o /tmp/volcano-agent-scheduler ./cmd/agentd\n\n      - name: Setup Python\n        uses: actions/setup-python@v5\n        with:\n          python-version: ${{ env.PYTHON_VERSION }}\n\n      - name: Build Python packages\n        run: |\n          pip install build\n          python -m build sdk-python/\n```\n\n### 3. CD 发布流水线 (cd.yml)\n\n```yaml\n# .github/workflows/cd.yml\nname: CD\n\non:\n  push:\n    branches: [main]\n    tags:\n      - 'v*'\n\nenv:\n  REGISTRY: ghcr.io\n  IMAGE_NAMESPACE: volcano-sh\n\npermissions:\n  contents: read\n  packages: write\n  id-token: write\n\njobs:\n  build-and-push-images:\n    name: Build and Push Images\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    if: github.event_name == 'push' && startsWith(github.ref, 'refs/tags/v')\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Setup Docker Buildx\n        uses: docker/setup-buildx-action@v3\n\n      - name: Login to GHCR\n        uses: docker/login-action@v3\n        with:\n          registry: ${{ env.REGISTRY }}\n          username: ${{ github.actor }}\n          password: ${{ secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN }}\n\n      - name: Extract metadata\n        id: meta\n        uses: docker/metadata-action@v5\n        with:\n          images: |\n            ${{ env.REGISTRY }}/${{ env.IMAGE_NAMESPACE }}/workloadmanager\n            ${{ env.REGISTRY }}/${{ env.IMAGE_NAMESPACE }}/router\n            ${{ env.REGISTRY }}/${{ env.IMAGE_NAMESPACE }}/volcano-agent-scheduler\n          tags: |\n            type=semver,pattern={{version}}\n            type=semver,pattern={{major}}.{{minor}}\n            type=sha,prefix=\n\n      - name: Build and push Workload Manager\n        uses: docker/build-push-action@v5\n        with:\n          context: .\n          file: deployment/docker/Dockerfile.workloadmanager\n          push: true\n          tags: ${{ steps.meta.outputs.tags }}\n          platforms: linux/amd64,linux/arm64\n          cache-from: type=gha\n          cache-to: type=gha,mode=max\n\n      - name: Build and push Router\n        uses: docker/build-push-action@v5\n        with:\n          context: .\n          file: deployment/docker/Dockerfile.router\n          push: true\n          tags: ${{ steps.meta.outputs.tags }}\n          platforms: linux/amd64,linux/arm64\n          cache-from: type=gha\n          cache-to: type=gha,mode=max\n\n      - name: Build and push Volcano Agent Scheduler\n        uses: docker/build-push-action@v5\n        with:\n          context: .\n          file: deployment/docker/Dockerfile.volcano-agent-scheduler\n          push: true\n          tags: ${{ steps.meta.outputs.tags }}\n          platforms: linux/amd64,linux/arm64\n          cache-from: type=gha\n          cache-to: type=gha,mode=max\n\n  publish-helm-chart:\n    name: Publish Helm Chart\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    needs: build-and-push-images\n    if: github.event_name == 'push' && startsWith(github.ref, 'refs/tags/v')\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n        with:\n          fetch-depth: 0\n\n      - name: Setup Helm\n        uses: azure/setup-helm@v3\n        with:\n          version: v3.14.0\n\n      - name: Configure Git\n        run: |\n          git config user.name \"$GITHUB_ACTOR\"\n          git config user.email \"$GITHUB_ACTOR@users.noreply.github.com\"\n\n      - name: Run chart-releaser\n        uses: helm/chart-releaser-action@v1.6.0\n        with:\n          charts_dir: manifests/\n        env:\n          CR_TOKEN: \"${{ secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN }}\"\n```\n\n### 4. 安全扫描 (security-scan.yml)\n\n```yaml\n# .github/workflows/security-scan.yml\nname: Security Scan\n\non:\n  push:\n    branches: [main, develop]\n  pull_request:\n    branches: [main]\n  schedule:\n    - cron: '0 2 * * 1' # Weekly on Monday\n\npermissions:\n  contents: read\n  security-events: write\n  actions: read\n\njobs:\n  trivy-scan:\n    name: Trivy Container Scan\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Build images for scanning\n        run: |\n          docker build -f deployment/docker/Dockerfile.workloadmanager -t localhost/workloadmanager:scan .\n          docker build -f deployment/docker/Dockerfile.router -t localhost/router:scan .\n          docker build -f deployment/docker/Dockerfile.volcano-agent-scheduler -t localhost/volcano-agent-scheduler:scan .\n\n      - name: Run Trivy scanner\n        uses: aquasecurity/trivy-action@master\n        with:\n          image-ref: localhost/workloadmanager:scan\n          format: 'sarif'\n          output: 'trivy-workloadmanager.sarif'\n          severity: 'CRITICAL,HIGH'\n\n      - name: Upload Trivy results\n        uses: github/codeql-action/upload-sarif@v3\n        with:\n          sarif_file: 'trivy-workloadmanager.sarif'\n\n  codeql-scan:\n    name: CodeQL Code Scan\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Setup Go\n        uses: actions/setup-go@v5\n        with:\n          go-version: '1.24'\n\n      - name: Initialize CodeQL\n        uses: github/codeql-action/init@v3\n        with:\n          languages: go, python\n          queries: security-extended\n\n      - name: Autobuild\n        uses: github/codeql-action/autobuild@v3\n\n      - name: Perform CodeQL Analysis\n        uses: github/codeql-action/analyze@v3\n        with:\n          category: \"/language:go,python\"\n\n  go-security:\n    name: Go Security Scan\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Setup Go\n        uses: actions/setup-go@v5\n        with:\n          go-version: '1.24'\n\n      - name: Run gosec\n        uses: securego/gosec@master\n        with:\n          args: ./...\n\n  dependency-audit:\n    name: Python Dependency Audit\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Setup Python\n        uses: actions/setup-python@v5\n        with:\n          python-version: '3.11'\n\n      - name: Install audit tools\n        run: pip install safety pip-audit\n\n      - name: Run safety check\n        run: safety check -r sdk-python/requirements.txt\n\n      - name: Run pip-audit\n        run: pip-audit -r sdk-python/requirements.txt\n```\n\n### 5. 文档部署 (docs.yml)\n\n```yaml\n# .github/workflows/docs.yml\nname: Docs\n\non:\n  push:\n    branches: [main]\n    paths:\n      - 'docs/**'\n      - 'website/**'\n\npermissions:\n  contents: read\n  pages: write\n  id-token: write\n\njobs:\n  build-and-deploy:\n    name: Build and Deploy Docs\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    environment:\n      name: github-pages\n      url: ${{ steps.deployment.outputs.page_url }}\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Setup Node.js\n        uses: actions/setup-node@v4\n        with:\n          node-version: '20'\n          cache: 'npm'\n          cache-dependency-path: website/package-lock.json\n\n      - name: Install dependencies\n        run: cd website && npm ci\n\n      - name: Build site\n        run: cd website && npm run build\n\n      - name: Setup Pages\n        uses: actions/configure-pages@v4\n\n      - name: Upload artifact\n        uses: actions/upload-pages-artifact@v3\n        with:\n          path: './website/build'\n\n      - name: Deploy to GitHub Pages\n        id: deployment\n        uses: actions/deploy-pages@v4\n```\n\n### 6. 多架构构建 (multi-arch-build.yml)\n\n```yaml\n# .github/workflows/multi-arch-build.yml\nname: Multi-Arch Build\n\non:\n  push:\n    branches: [main]\n    paths:\n      - 'cmd/**'\n      - 'pkg/**'\n      - 'deployment/docker/**'\n  pull_request:\n    paths:\n      - 'cmd/**'\n      - 'pkg/**'\n      - 'deployment/docker/**'\n\npermissions:\n  contents: read\n\njobs:\n  build-multi-arch:\n    name: Build Multi-Arch Images\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    strategy:\n      matrix:\n        component: [workloadmanager, router, volcano-agent-scheduler]\n        platform: [linux/amd64, linux/arm64]\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Setup Docker Buildx\n        uses: docker/setup-buildx-action@v3\n\n      - name: Build ${{ matrix.component }} for ${{ matrix.platform }}\n        run: |\n          docker buildx build \\\n            --platform ${{ matrix.platform }} \\\n            -t ghcr.io/volcano-sh/${{ matrix.component }}:${{ github.sha }} \\\n            --load \\\n            -f deployment/docker/Dockerfile.${{ matrix.component }} \\\n            .\n\n      - name: Test image\n        run: |\n          docker run --rm ghcr.io/volcano-sh/${{ matrix.component }}:${{ github.sha }} --help\n```\n\n### 7. 端到端测试 (e2e-test.yml)\n\n```yaml\n# .github/workflows/e2e-test.yml\nname: E2E Test\n\non:\n  pull_request:\n    branches: [main]\n    paths:\n      - 'cmd/**'\n      - 'pkg/**'\n      - 'manifests/**'\n      - 'testing/**'\n\npermissions:\n  contents: read\n\njobs:\n  e2e-test:\n    name: E2E Test\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    timeout-minutes: 30\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Setup Go\n        uses: actions/setup-go@v5\n        with:\n          go-version: '1.24'\n\n      - name: Setup Python\n        uses: actions/setup-python@v5\n        with:\n          python-version: '3.11'\n\n      - name: Setup Kind\n        uses: helm/kind-action@v1.9.0\n        with:\n          version: v0.20.0\n          node_image: kindest/node:v1.28.0\n\n      - name: Install Redis\n        run: |\n          kubectl apply -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/bitnami/charts/main/bitnami/redis/templates/deployment.yaml\n          kubectl wait --for=condition=available deployment/redis --timeout=120s\n\n      - name: Install AgentCube\n        run: |\n          helm install agentcube manifests/ \\\n            --set image.repository=localhost:5000 \\\n            --set redis.host=redis.default.svc.cluster.local\n\n      - name: Wait for deployment\n        run: |\n          kubectl wait --for=condition=available deployment/workloadmanager --timeout=300s\n          kubectl wait --for=condition=available deployment/router --timeout=300s\n\n      - name: Run E2E tests\n        run: |\n          pip install pytest\n          pytest testing/e2e/ -v\n\n      - name: Collect logs on failure\n        if: failure()\n        run: |\n          kubectl get pods -A\n          kubectl logs -l app=workloadmanager\n          kubectl logs -l app=router\n```\n\n### 8. 夜间构建 (nightly-build.yml)\n\n```yaml\n# .github/workflows/nightly-build.yml\nname: Nightly Build\n\non:\n  schedule:\n    - cron: '0 2 * * *' # Daily at 2 AM UTC\n  workflow_dispatch:\n\npermissions:\n  contents: read\n  packages: write\n\njobs:\n  nightly-build:\n    name: Nightly Build\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Setup Docker Buildx\n        uses: docker/setup-buildx-action@v3\n\n      - name: Login to GHCR\n        uses: docker/login-action@v3\n        with:\n          registry: ghcr.io\n          username: ${{ github.actor }}\n          password: ${{ secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN }}\n\n      - name: Build and push nightly images\n        run: |\n          make docker-build-all\n          make docker-push-all\n        env:\n          DOCKER_TAG: nightly-${{ github.run_id }}\n```\n\n### 9. PR 验证 (pr-validation.yml)\n\n```yaml\n# .github/workflows/pr-validation.yml\nname: PR Validation\n\non:\n  pull_request_target:\n    types: [opened, edited, synchronize, reopened, labeled]\n\npermissions:\n  pull-requests: write\n  contents: read\n\njobs:\n  validate-pr-title:\n    name: Validate PR Title\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - name: Check PR title\n        uses: amannn/action-semantic-pull-request@v5\n        env:\n          GITHUB_TOKEN: ${{ secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN }}\n        with:\n          types: |\n            feat\n            fix\n            docs\n            style\n            refactor\n            perf\n            test\n            build\n            ci\n            chore\n            revert\n          requireScope: false\n\n  validate-pr-body:\n    name: Validate PR Body\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - name: Check PR has description\n        uses: actions/github-script@v7\n        with:\n          script: |\n            const pr = context.payload.pull_request;\n            if (!pr.body || pr.body.trim() === '') {\n              core.setFailed('PR description is required');\n            }\n\n  check-issues-linked:\n    name: Check Issues Linked\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - name: Check for linked issues\n        uses: actions/github-script@v7\n        with:\n          script: |\n            const pr = context.payload.pull_request;\n            const body = pr.body || '';\n            if (!body.match(/(close|closes|closed|fix|fixes|fixed|resolve|resolves|resolved)\\s#(\\d+)/i)) {\n              console.log('No linked issues found (optional)');\n            }\n```\n\n### 10. Release 发布 (release.yml)\n\n```yaml\n# .github/workflows/release.yml\nname: Release\n\non:\n  push:\n    tags:\n      - 'v*'\n\npermissions:\n  contents: write\n  packages: write\n  id-token: write\n\njobs:\n  create-release:\n    name: Create Release\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    outputs:\n      upload_url: ${{ steps.create_release.outputs.upload_url }}\n      version: ${{ steps.get_version.outputs.version }}\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n        with:\n          fetch-depth: 0\n\n      - name: Get version\n        id: get_version\n        run: echo \"version=${GITHUB_REF#refs/tags/}\" >> $GITHUB_OUTPUT\n\n      - name: Generate changelog\n        uses: mikepenz/release-changelog-builder-action@v4\n        id: changelog\n        with:\n          configuration: .github/release-config.json\n\n      - name: Create Release\n        id: create_release\n        uses: softprops/action-gh-release@v1\n        with:\n          body: ${{ steps.changelog.outputs.changelog }}\n          draft: false\n          prerelease: false\n        env:\n          GITHUB_TOKEN: ${{ secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN }}\n\n  publish-python-sdk:\n    name: Publish Python SDK\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    needs: create-release\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Setup Python\n        uses: actions/setup-python@v5\n        with:\n          python-version: '3.11'\n\n      - name: Install build tools\n        run: pip install build twine\n\n      - name: Build package\n        run: python -m build sdk-python/\n\n      - name: Publish to PyPI\n        uses: pypa/gh-action-pypi-publish@release/v1\n        with:\n          packages-dir: sdk-python/dist/\n          password: ${{ secrets.PYPI_API_TOKEN }}\n\n  publish-cli-tool:\n    name: Publish CLI Tool\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    needs: create-release\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Setup Python\n        uses: actions/setup-python@v5\n        with:\n          python-version: '3.11'\n\n      - name: Install build tools\n        run: pip install build twine\n\n      - name: Build CLI\n        run: python -m build cmd/cli/\n\n      - name: Publish to PyPI\n        uses: pypa/gh-action-pypi-publish@release/v1\n        with:\n          packages-dir: cmd/cli/dist/\n          password: ${{ secrets.PYPI_API_TOKEN }}\n\n  sign-artifacts:\n    name: Sign Artifacts\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    needs: create-release\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Setup cosign\n        uses: sigstore/cosign-installer@v3\n\n      - name: Sign images\n        run: |\n          cosign sign ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager:${{ needs.create-release.outputs.version }}\n          cosign sign ghcr.io/volcano-sh/router:${{ needs.create-release.outputs.version }}\n          cosign sign ghcr.io/volcano-sh/volcano-agent-scheduler:${{ needs.create-release.outputs.version }}\n        env:\n          COSIGN_EXPERIMENTAL: \"true\"\n```\n\n### 11. 依赖审查 (dependency-review.yml)\n\n```yaml\n# .github/workflows/dependency-review.yml\nname: Dependency Review\n\non:\n  pull_request:\n    branches: [main, develop]\n\npermissions:\n  contents: read\n\njobs:\n  dependency-review:\n    name: Dependency Review\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Dependency Review\n        uses: actions/dependency-review-action@v4\n        with:\n          fail-on-severity: high\n          deny-licenses: GPL-3.0, AGPL-3.0\n\n  go-dependency-check:\n    name: Go Dependency Check\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Setup Go\n        uses: actions/setup-go@v5\n        with:\n          go-version: '1.24'\n\n      - name: Run govulncheck\n        run: |\n          go install golang.org/x/vuln/cmd/govulncheck@latest\n          govulncheck ./...\n\n  python-dependency-check:\n    name: Python Dependency Check\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Setup Python\n        uses: actions/setup-python@v5\n        with:\n          python-version: '3.11'\n\n      - name: Run pip-audit\n        run: |\n          pip install pip-audit\n          pip-audit -r sdk-python/requirements.txt\n          pip-audit -r cmd/cli/requirements.txt\n```\n\n### 12. Stale 管理 (stale.yml)\n\n```yaml\n# .github/workflows/stale.yml\nname: Stale\n\non:\n  schedule:\n    - cron: '0 0 * * *' # Daily\n  workflow_dispatch:\n\npermissions:\n  issues: write\n  pull-requests: write\n\njobs:\n  stale:\n    name: Close Stale Issues and PRs\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - name: Close stale issues and PRs\n        uses: actions/stale@v9\n        with:\n          stale-issue-message: 'This issue has been automatically marked as stale because it has not had recent activity. It will be closed if no further activity occurs.'\n          stale-pr-message: 'This PR has been automatically marked as stale because it has not had recent activity. It will be closed if no further activity occurs.'\n          close-issue-message: 'This issue was closed because it has been stalled for 30 days with no activity.'\n          close-pr-message: 'This PR was closed because it has been stalled for 30 days with no activity.'\n          days-before-issue-stale: 60\n          days-before-pr-stale: 30\n          days-before-issue-close: 90\n          days-before-pr-close: 60\n          exempt-issue-labels: 'bug,enhancement,help wanted,good first issue'\n          exempt-pr-labels: 'bug,enhancement,help wanted'\n          stale-issue-label: 'stale'\n          stale-pr-label: 'stale'\n          remove-stale-when-updated: true\n          operations-per-run: 100\n```\n\n### 13. 自动标签 (labeler.yml)\n\n```yaml\n# .github/workflows/labeler.yml\nname: Labeler\n\non:\n  - pull_request_target\n\npermissions:\n  contents: read\n  pull-requests: write\n\njobs:\n  label:\n    name: Apply Labels\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - name: Apply Labels\n        uses: actions/labeler@v5\n        with:\n          repo-token: \"${{ secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN }}\"\n          configuration-path: .github/labeler.yml\n```\n\n### 14. Dependabot 配置 (dependabot.yml)\n\n```yaml\n# .github/dependabot.yml\nversion: 2\nupdates:\n  # Go dependencies\n  - package-ecosystem: \"gomod\"\n    directory: \"/\"\n    schedule:\n      interval: \"weekly\"\n      day: \"monday\"\n      time: \"02:00\"\n    open-pull-requests-limit: 10\n    labels:\n      - \"dependencies\"\n      - \"go\"\n    commit-message:\n      prefix: \"chore(go)\"\n      include: \"scope\"\n    groups:\n      k8s-io:\n        patterns:\n          - \"k8s.io/*\"\n          - \"sigs.k8s.io/*\"\n      volcano:\n        patterns:\n          - \"volcano.sh/*\"\n\n  # Python dependencies\n  - package-ecosystem: \"pip\"\n    directory: \"/sdk-python\"\n    schedule:\n      interval: \"weekly\"\n      day: \"monday\"\n      time: \"02:00\"\n    open-pull-requests-limit: 10\n    labels:\n      - \"dependencies\"\n      - \"python\"\n    commit-message:\n      prefix: \"chore(python)\"\n      include: \"scope\"\n\n  - package-ecosystem: \"pip\"\n    directory: \"/cmd/cli\"\n    schedule:\n      interval: \"weekly\"\n      day: \"monday\"\n      time: \"02:00\"\n    open-pull-requests-limit: 10\n    labels:\n      - \"dependencies\"\n      - \"python\"\n    commit-message:\n      prefix: \"chore(cli)\"\n      include: \"scope\"\n\n  # GitHub Actions\n  - package-ecosystem: \"github-actions\"\n    directory: \"/\"\n    schedule:\n      interval: \"weekly\"\n      day: \"monday\"\n      time: \"02:00\"\n    open-pull-requests-limit: 10\n    labels:\n      - \"dependencies\"\n      - \"github-actions\"\n    commit-message:\n      prefix: \"chore(actions)\"\n      include: \"scope\"\n\n  # Docker\n  - package-ecosystem: \"docker\"\n    directory: \"/deployment/docker\"\n    schedule:\n      interval: \"weekly\"\n      day: \"monday\"\n      time: \"02:00\"\n    open-pull-requests-limit: 5\n    labels:\n      - \"dependencies\"\n      - \"docker\"\n    commit-message:\n      prefix: \"chore(docker)\"\n      include: \"scope\"\n```\n\n### 15. 标签规则 (labeler.yml)\n\n```yaml\n# .github/labeler.yml\n# Automatically apply labels to PRs based on file patterns\n\ngo:\n  - changed-files:\n      - any-glob-to-any-file:\n          - cmd/**/*.go\n          - pkg/**/*.go\n          - \"*.go\"\n          - go.mod\n          - go.sum\n\npython:\n  - changed-files:\n      - any-glob-to-any-file:\n          - sdk-python/**/*.py\n          - cmd/cli/**/*.py\n          - \"**/requirements.txt\"\n\ndocumentation:\n  - changed-files:\n      - any-glob-to-any-file:\n          - docs/**/*\n          - website/**/*\n          - \"*.md\"\n          - README.md\n\nhelm:\n  - changed-files:\n      - any-glob-to-any-file:\n          - manifests/**/*.yaml\n          - manifests/**/*.tpl\n          - manifests/Chart.yaml\n          - manifests/values.yaml\n\ndocker:\n  - changed-files:\n      - any-glob-to-any-file:\n          - deployment/docker/**/*\n          - \"**/Dockerfile*\"\n          - .dockerignore\n\nci-cd:\n  - changed-files:\n      - any-glob-to-any-file:\n          - .github/workflows/**/*\n          - .github/dependabot.yml\n          - .github/labeler.yml\n\ntests:\n  - changed-files:\n      - any-glob-to-any-file:\n          - testing/**/*\n          - \"**/*_test.go\"\n          - \"**/test_*.py\"\n\nconfiguration:\n  - changed-files:\n      - any-glob-to-any-file:\n          - \"*.yaml\"\n          - \"*.yml\"\n          - \"*.toml\"\n          - Makefile\n          - .golangci.yml\n```\n\n### 16. 代码所有者 (CODEOWNERS)\n\n```\n# .github/CODEOWNERS\n# Code owners for automatic review assignment\n\n# Default owners\n* @agentcube-maintainers\n\n# Go code\n/cmd/ @agentcube-go-team\n/pkg/ @agentcube-go-team\n\n# Python SDK and CLI\n/sdk-python/ @agentcube-python-team\n/cmd/cli/ @agentcube-python-team\n\n# Kubernetes manifests\n/manifests/ @agentcube-k8s-team\n\n# Documentation\n/docs/ @agentcube-docs-team\n/website/ @agentcube-docs-team\n\n# CI/CD\n.github/ @agentcube-devops-team\n\n# Docker\n/deployment/docker/ @agentcube-devops-team\n\n# Tests\n/testing/ @agentcube-qa-team\n```\n\n## Impact Analysis\n\n### 依赖影响\n\n| 依赖项 | 版本 | 用途 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| GitHub Actions | - | CI/CD 平台 |\n| Go | 1.24 | 应用编译 |\n| Python | 3.11 | SDK/CLI 构建 |\n| Node.js | 20 | 文档构建 |\n| Docker | 预装 | 镜像构建 |\n| Helm | 3.14+ | Chart 打包 |\n| Kind | 0.20+ | E2E 测试集群 |\n| Trivy | latest | 安全扫描 |\n| CodeQL | v3 | 代码分析 |\n\n### 模块依赖关系\n\n```\n.github/\n├── workflows/\n│   ├── ci.yml                      # 依赖：Go, Python, Helm, Redis\n│   ├── cd.yml                      # 依赖：AR-032 (Dockerfile), AR-033 (Makefile)\n│   ├── security-scan.yml           # 依赖：Trivy, CodeQL, gosec\n│   ├── docs.yml                    # 依赖：Node.js, Docusaurus\n│   ├── multi-arch-build.yml        # 依赖：Docker Buildx\n│   ├── e2e-test.yml                # 依赖：Kind, Helm, Redis\n│   ├── nightly-build.yml           # 依赖：AR-033 (Makefile)\n│   ├── pr-validation.yml           # 依赖：GitHub API\n│   ├── release.yml                 # 依赖：PyPI, GHCR, cosign\n│   ├── dependency-review.yml       # 依赖：govulncheck, pip-audit\n│   ├── stale.yml                   # 依赖：GitHub API\n│   └── labeler.yml                 # 依赖：labeler action\n├── dependabot.yml                  # 依赖：GitHub API\n├── labeler.yml                     # 依赖：labeler action\n└── CODEOWNERS                      # 依赖：GitHub teams\n```\n\n### 向后兼容性\n\n- 首次实现，无破坏性变更\n- 工作流设计为增量式采纳，团队可选择性启用\n- 依赖自动更新（Dependabot）确保 Action 版本更新\n\n### 成本影响\n\n| 资源 | 月度估算 | 备注 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| GitHub Actions Minutes | 3000 分钟 | 免费额度 2000 分钟/月，超出需付费 |\n| Storage (Packages) | 5 GB | GHCR 存储，免费 50GB |\n| Actions Runners | Self-hosted (可选) | 减少成本，提高速度 |\n\n### 安全影响\n\n- **Positive**: 自动化安全扫描，及时检测漏洞\n- **Positive**: 依赖审查，阻止不安全依赖\n- **Positive**: CodeQL 分析，发现代码安全问题\n- **Consideration**: GHCR Token 权限管理，需最小权限原则\n- **Consideration**: PyPI Token 存储，需使用 GitHub Secrets\n\n## Alternatives Considered\n\n### 方案 1: 使用 CircleCI 替代 GitHub Actions\n\n**优点:**\n- 更灵活的配置选项\n- 更好的并行执行能力\n- 更便宜的定价\n\n**缺点:**\n- 需要额外注册和配置\n- 与 GitHub 集成度低\n- 学习成本增加\n\n**决策:** 使用 GitHub Actions，保持与 GitHub 深度集成。\n\n### 方案 2: 使用 Jenkins 自建 CI/CD\n\n**优点:**\n- 完全控制\n- 无使用限制\n- 丰富的插件生态\n\n**缺点:**\n- 维护成本高\n- 需要基础设施\n- 配置复杂\n\n**决策:** 使用 GitHub Actions，减少运维负担。\n\n### 方案 3: 单个工作流文件（monolithic workflow）\n\n**优点:**\n- 配置集中\n- 易于理解整体流程\n\n**缺点:**\n- 文件过大难以维护\n- 无法独立触发/调试\n- 执行效率低\n\n**决策:** 采用模块化设计，每个工作流独立职责。\n\n### 方案 4: 使用 GitLab CI/CD\n\n**优点:**\n- 原生集成 GitLab\n- 强大的 YAML 语法\n- 免费额度较高\n\n**缺点:**\n- 需要迁移代码仓库\n- 团队学习成本\n- 生态锁定\n\n**决策:** 保持 GitHub，使用 GitHub Actions。\n\n### 方案 5: 手动发布流程\n\n**优点:**\n- 完全控制发布过程\n- 无需配置工作流\n\n**缺点:**\n- 容易出错\n- 无法追溯\n- 效率低下\n\n**决策:** 自动化发布，提高可靠性和效率。\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### 工作流验证\n\n1. **语法验证** - 使用 `actionlint` 验证 YAML 语法\n2. **本地测试** - 使用 `act` 工具在本地运行工作流\n3. **Dry Run** - 在 PR 中测试工作流触发\n\n### 集成测试\n\n1. **CI 流水线测试** - 验证 lint, test, build 全部通过\n2. **CD 流水线测试** - 在 staging 环境验证发布\n3. **E2E 测试** - 验证 Kind 集群中完整部署\n\n### 安全测试\n\n1. **权限验证** - 验证 GITHUB_TOKEN 权限最小化\n2. **Secret 测试** - 验证 Secrets 未被泄露\n3. **依赖扫描** - 验证 Trivy/CodeQL 能检测问题\n\n### 性能测试\n\n1. **并行执行测试** - 验证并发作业不冲突\n2. **缓存测试** - 验证 Docker/Go 缓存命中率\n3. **超时测试** - 验证长运行作业有超时保护\n\n### 测试覆盖目标\n\n- 工作流语法：100% 有效\n- CI 触发：100%（push, PR）\n- CD 触发：100%（tag）\n- 安全扫描：100%（定期 + PR）\n- 文档部署：100%（main 分支）\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] `ci.yml` 在 PR 和 push 事件中成功触发\n- [ ] `cd.yml` 在 tag 推送时成功发布镜像\n- [ ] `security-scan.yml` 成功运行 Trivy 和 CodeQL\n- [ ] `docs.yml` 成功部署文档到 GitHub Pages\n- [ ] `multi-arch-build.yml` 成功构建 amd64 和 arm64 镜像\n- [ ] `e2e-test.yml` 在 Kind 集群中成功运行 E2E 测试\n- [ ] `nightly-build.yml` 按计划触发夜间构建\n- [ ] `pr-validation.yml` 验证 PR 标题和描述\n- [ ] `release.yml` 成功创建 GitHub Release 并发布 PyPI 包\n- [ ] `dependency-review.yml` 成功检测依赖漏洞\n- [ ] `stale.yml` 成功标记和关闭 stale 问题/PR\n- [ ] `labeler.yml` 成功自动应用标签\n- [ ] `dependabot.yml` 成功创建依赖更新 PR\n- [ ] `labeler.yml` 文件规则正确匹配\n- [ ] `CODEOWNERS` 正确分配审查者\n- [ ] 所有工作流通过语法验证（actionlint）\n- [ ] 所有 Secrets 配置正确\n- [ ] 文档完整（使用说明、故障排查）\n\n## Dependencies\n\n### 必需依赖\n- GitHub 仓库\n- GitHub Actions 启用\n- GHCR 访问权限\n- PyPI 账号（发布 SDK/CLI）\n\n### 可选依赖\n- Codecov 账号（测试覆盖率）\n- Self-hosted Runner（可选，降低成本）\n- Slack/Discord Webhook（通知）\n\n### 被依赖\n- AR-032 (Dockerfile 多阶段构建) - 提供 Dockerfile\n- AR-033 (Makefile 构建目标) - 提供 make 命令\n- AR-030 (Helm Chart) - 提供 manifests/\n\n## Migration Notes\n\n### 从零到 CI/CD\n\n1. **初始设置**\n   - 创建 `.github/workflows/` 目录\n   - 复制所有工作流文件\n   - 配置 Dependabot 和 CODEOWNERS\n\n2. **配置 Secrets**\n   ```bash\n   # 必需配置\n   GITHUB_TOKEN (自动提供)\n   PYPI_API_TOKEN (PyPI 发布)\n   ```\n\n3. **启用工作流**\n   - 检查 GitHub Settings → Actions\n   - 确保 Actions 已启用\n   - 配置权限设置\n\n4. **首次运行**\n   - 创建测试 PR 验证 CI\n   - 创建测试 tag 验证 CD\n   - 检查所有工作流运行状态\n\n### 破坏性变更\n无 - 首次实现。\n\n### 行为变更\n- PR 必须通过 CI 检查才能合并\n- Tag 推送自动触发发布\n- 依赖自动更新\n\n## Open Questions\n\n1. 是否需要集成 Slack/Discord 通知？\n2. 是否需要支持多环境部署（dev/staging/prod）？\n3. 是否需要配置自托管 Runner 以降低成本？\n4. 是否需要集成 SonarQube 代码质量分析？\n5. 是否需要配置性能基准测试？\n\n## References\n\n- `project.md` - AgentCube 项目上下文\n- `changes/AR-032/proposal.md` - Dockerfile 多阶段构建\n- `changes/AR-033/proposal.md` - Makefile 构建目标\n- GitHub Actions Documentation: https://docs.github.com/en/actions\n- GitHub Actions Marketplace: https://github.com/marketplace?type=actions\n- Trivy Documentation: https://aquasecurity.github.io/trivy/\n- CodeQL Documentation: https://codeql.github.com/\n- Dependabot Documentation: https://docs.github.com/en/code-security/dependabot\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-034/proposal.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-034/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775883070515,"end":1775883070529}}}}
