{"type":"text","timestamp":1775883077406,"sessionID":"ses_285222e43ffe4HfnmS1LBKuzWs","part":{"id":"prt_d7ae1365d001pDGIiXF43ACdDv","messageID":"msg_d7ae12c83001uVSUSHPPofNcUt","sessionID":"ses_285222e43ffe4HfnmS1LBKuzWs","type":"text","text":"Done. Created `changes/AR-034/proposal.md` with 12 GitHub Actions workflows:\n\n1. **ci.yml** - CI 主流水线 (lint, test, build)\n2. **cd.yml** - CD 发布流水线 (镜像推送、Helm 发布)\n3. **security-scan.yml** - 安全扫描 (Trivy, CodeQL, gosec)\n4. **docs.yml** - 文档部署到 GitHub Pages\n5. **multi-arch-build.yml** - 多架构镜像构建\n6. **e2e-test.yml** - Kind 集群端到端测试\n7. **nightly-build.yml** - 每日夜间构建\n8. **pr-validation.yml** - PR 标题/描述验证\n9. **release.yml** - GitHub Release + PyPI 发布\n10. **dependency-review.yml** - 依赖安全审查\n11. **stale.yml** - Stale 问题/PR 管理\n12. **labeler.yml** - 自动标签\n\nPlus supporting configs: `dependabot.yml`, `labeler.yml`, `CODEOWNERS`","time":{"start":1775883077404,"end":1775883077404}}}
